 </p>
 </div>

 <div>
 <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Which platform is better for beginners?</h3>
 <p class="text-neutral-300">
 <strong>See Guru is often better for beginners</strong> because the tutors are patient and you can practice at your own pace without pressure. Preply can work well too if you find an experienced tutor who specializes in beginners.
 </p>
 </div>

 <div>
