 <!-- Ad Unit -->
 <div class="mb-8">
 <AdUnit slot="compare-3" />
 </div>

 <!-- Final Verdict -->
 <section class="bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 mb-8">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Final Verdict</h2>
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">See Guru and Preply serve different needs in the English learning market. See Guru wins for learners who want affordable, unlimited practice at any time of day. Preply wins for those who value human connection, structured curriculum, and cultural exchange.
 </p>
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">If we had to pick one platform for most learners, we would choose <strong>See Guru</strong> for its accessibility and value. Pay-per-lesson flexibility starting at $5/hr, with three free trial lessons first, makes it easier to build consistent learning habits without any subscription commitment.
 </p>
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">However, serious learners should consider using both platforms together. Start your day with See Guru for warm-up conversations, then book a weekly Preply session for deeper feedback and structured practice.
 </p>

 <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
 <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Ready to Start Learning?</h3>
 <p class="text-green-100 mb-4">Try See Guru today and get 3 free trial lessons with certified human tutors, starting at just $5 per hour.</p>
 <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-block bg-slate-900/60 text-green-700 font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-50 transition-colors">Start Free Practice Now</a>
